snippet.textDisplay:
Linkin Park has redefined a new era for Alternative Rock fusing amazing rap vocals from Mike and Chester screaming his lungs out making them one of the emerging and influential rock band of the 21st century . Mike and Chester were Yin and Yang to the group always re inventing themselves with every album and pushing their boundaries by collaborating and experimenting with musicians of different Genres . Though most of their music lyrics may be based on battles with own demons , substance abuse or any other trauma , Your music is a miracle drug for those who have experienced trauma in any form and has proved a cathartic effect to overcome my past trauma. Thanks for bringing awareness for mental health and attempting to remove the stigma or taboo attached to it. Its overdue that you should be inducted in the Rock Hall of Fame.
Be Safe and Stay Inspired .
